sentences: Sarah Beth Tomberlin (born April 6, 1995), known mononymously as Tomberlin, is an American folk musician and singer-songwriter based in Louisville, Kentucky.
Tomberlin released her debut full-length album in 2018 on Saddle Creek Records, titled At Weddings.
On August 18, 2020, Tomberlin announced a new EP called Projections, due out October 16, 2020, alongside the release of a Busy Philipps-directed music video for the song "Wasted."
